---
name: Woodcut
description: Style preset — Woodcut
tags: [style, retro, aspect-auto]
---
Render as a medieval woodcut or linocut print on an aged parchment or cream-colored background. Use bold black carved lines with visible wood-grain texture in the strokes. Use cross-hatching for shading and fills. Text should appear in a blackletter or old-style serif typeface. Shapes should have a rough, hand-carved quality. Optionally add a single spot color (a deep red or ochre) for emphasis on key elements. The result should look like a page from an illuminated technical manuscript -- ancient, authoritative, and delightfully absurd as a format for modern tech diagrams.
